name: UISpringLoadedInteractionEffectState
desc: The spring-loaded interaction states that determine the style of the interaction view.

items.name: case activated
items.desc: An interaction state that indicates that the view was spring loaded.

items.name: case activating
items.desc: An interaction state that indicates that spring loading is about to start.

items.name: case inactive
items.desc: An interaction state that indicates that spring loading is not engaged.

items.name: case possible
items.desc: An interaction state that indicates that spring loading is available.
